ritten about.\nThe department is reviewing its policy with regard to immunisation.', '关于;至于\n这个部门正在审度其有关疫苗接种的政策。'], ['PHRASE\nYou can use in this regard or in that regard to refer back to something that you have just said.\nIn this regard nothing has changed...\nI may have made a mistake in that regard.', '在这/那方面；就这/那一点\n在这方面没什么变化。\n我在那一点上可能已经犯了一个错误。']]}]